             was indicted for <rs id="t17750426-18-off85" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17750426-18-off85" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17750426-18-off85" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
