                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17750426-18-victim205 t17750426-18-viclabel87"></join>: a linen shirt, value three shillings, a check apron, value two-pence, and three linen towels, value two-pence, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17750426-18-victim207" type="victimName">
